<html xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_1_0.xsd">
<body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;  font-size: smaller;">
	<h1>Autocomplete Mixin</h1>
	This page demonstrates the Autocomplete Mixin.  It has been mixed into an ordinary TextField component.<br/> 
	As you type, Autocomplete issues <em>providecompletions</em> events which we handle by returning a list of partial matches.<br/><br/>

	<form t:type="form">
		Type in a country name:
		<input t:id="countryName" t:type="TextField" t:mixins="autocomplete"/>
	</form>

	References: 
	<a href="http://tapestry.apache.org/tapestry5/tapestry-core/ref/org/apache/tapestry5/corelib/mixins/Autocomplete.html">Autocomplete</a>,
